ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the Species at Risk Act (Chestnut-collared Longspur and Nine Other Wildlife Species)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 to the SPECIES AT RISK ACT in order to add nine new species to the list of wildlife species at risk, and reclassify the Chestnut-collared Longspur from a status of threatened to endangered.
